        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "E5 Enclave Incorporated is registered in SAM.gov with UEI H8NGXEYE2HH8 and CAGE Code 07E88. SAM.gov registration is active through August 4, 2026. The organization is eligible for federal contracts and grants in community development, education, food systems, and technology sectors."
      }
    },
