        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Libations is E5 Enclave's tribute portal for fallen movement heroes — individuals whose work, sacrifice, and vision shaped the conditions for what E5 is building. The inaugural tribute honors Andrew Joseph Jr., a Liberty City community member. The section is located at e5enclave.com/libations/."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How do I apply for a grant or contract with E5 Enclave as a partner?",
